NAME
   ORPGDAT_ALERT_THRESHOLD - ORPG Alet Threshold information

OUTPUT BY
       hci_alt(1)
       orpgalt(3)
       mnttsk_alerting(1) 

INPUT BY
       hci_alt(1) 
       orpgalt(3)

DESCRIPTION

    This data store is a replaceable LB that contains Alert Threshold adaptation
    data.  It is initialized from configuration data by the "iati" task. The LB
    contains 4 messages:
    
    ORPGALT_GROUP_MSG_ID - This message contains the alert threshold group
    	definitions.
    
    ORPGALT_CATEGORY_MSG_ID - This message contains the alert threshold
    	category information.
    
    ORPGALT_BASELINE_GROUP_MSG_ID - This message contains a backup copy of
    	message ORPGALT_GROUP_MSG_ID.
    
    ORPGALT_BASELINE_CATEGORY_MSG_ID - This message contains a backup copy of
    	message ORPGALT_CATEGORY_MSG_ID.
    

    NOTE: A copy of the alert threshold category message is stored in the
    legacy common block ALRTAD to support legacy algorithms.  Applications
    should use the ORPGALT family of functions in liborpg to guarantee both
    copies are synchronized.

